INSERT INTO products VALUES("81","53","The Hunting Buddy","\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"3\"><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><i>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY&nbsp;</i></font></strong><em>(patent pending)</em><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><i>&nbsp;</i></font></strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">is\nby far the most versatile product that we have created!&nbsp; It is\nthe toughest and most multifaceted mobile</font><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\n</font></strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">hunting blind on\nthe market.&nbsp; It\'s the safest and most comfortable way to\ntransport hunters to the field, as well as your personal dog\ntrailer.&nbsp; It is also the roughest and toughest utility trailer\nfor your hunting land, ranch or farm.&nbsp; While you are on your\nranch, farm or hunting property</font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>\nTHE HUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\ncan be pulled from either the front or the back and can be pulled\nbehind a large ATV, Side by Side, hunting truck/jeep or even by your\nown personal vehicle.&nbsp; As mentioned, </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"> is\nextremely versatile and serves as an incomparable hunting blind for\nthe following: deer, hogs, turkey, exotics, ducks and most all other\nbig game.&nbsp; </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\nwas also designed for the upland game hunter and their prized hunting\ndogs.&nbsp; We even designed </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"> to\ntransport most handicap hunters safely from camp to the field without\nhaving to get out until they return back to camp.&nbsp; While </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\noffers hunting and transportation for every hunter, it also\nconveniently includes a dry box, storage compartments and storage\nareas so that you can bring all required hunting equipment, supplies\nand tools with you.&nbsp;&nbsp;Due to&nbsp;the vast differences&nbsp;in\nbrush and terrain&nbsp;and the different types of game that&nbsp;will\nbe hunted, we offer&nbsp;a variety of popular camo patterns&nbsp;that\nwill come in the most durable fabric. Once in the perfect hunting\nspot and your favorite camo pattern has been placed over </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">,\nthe final touch can be applied (not required)....our revolutionary\n</font><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><i>BrusHolders\n</i></font></strong><em>(patent pending)</em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">.&nbsp;\nYou can now truly conceal yourself by brushing up </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\nwith the natural foliage from your actual location.&nbsp; When you\nneed a helping hand and need to trailer items around your farm, ranch\nor lease, you will have the perfect help, </font><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><i>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY. </i></font></strong><em> </em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">Our\nunmatched multi-window zipper design offers you the ability to hunt\nBig Game by firearm or by archery.&nbsp; We have cleverly configured\n</font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE HUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><em><font size=\"2\">\n</font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">to simply be\ntransformed into a duck blind with the ease of unzipping the duck\nwindow.&nbsp;&nbsp;There is also&nbsp;a matching tasseled window for\nyour prized retriever to do his or her thing in proud fashion.</font></font></font><br></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">It\nis the perfect way to bring that trophy or those birds that you just\nbagged back to camp.&nbsp; Need to fill corn, protein, hay, quail or\nturkey feeders?&nbsp; Need to collect firewood for that campfire?&nbsp;\nNeed something to haul those ranching supplies around on?</font></font></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"3\"><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">Simply\nremove the seats from </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\nand load her up.&nbsp; Hunting season or not&#8230;if it needs hauling on\nthat property&#8230;look no further... </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">!&nbsp;\nIt&nbsp;was also designed to quickly and easily move around so that\nyou can hunt from a variety of different places on your hunting land\nwithout the need&nbsp;for a permanent blind at each desired location.\n&nbsp;Also, if the game have become weary of your presence, simply\nmove it.&nbsp; Discovered a fresh rub line, a fresh scrape, observed\na trophy in a new area&#8230;again, move it.&nbsp; With the arrival of\nnew birds, the availability of water and food sources, old Mother\nNature or just out scouting, guess what&#8230;just move it! &nbsp;The\nversatility and uniqueness of this product will reduce costs\ntremendously for the hunter, not to mention the revenue stream it\nwill bring to the Professional Hunting Guide.&nbsp; You can use </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\n</font><em>(patent pending)</em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\nin so many different hunting scenarios and for so many different\nreasons. Rather than purchasing a separate deer blind, a hog blind, a\nduck blind, a field transporter, dog kennels and a small utility\ntrailer you can get all of that in one, </font><strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><i>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</i></font></strong><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\n</font><em><font size=\"2\">(</font></em><em>patent pending).</em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">&nbsp;\nOur unique rugged metal design makes it extremely easy to pull into\nthose remote and hard to get to locations without damaging it or\nadding expensive repair costs.&nbsp; </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE\nHUNTING BUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">\nwas carefully designed for everyone; the all around hunter, the\nprofessional hunter, the hunting family, the hunting group, the land\nowner and the Professional Hunting Guide.&nbsp; Hands down, this is\ntruly </font><em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\"><b>THE HUNTING\nBUDDY</b></font></em><font style=\"font-size: 13pt;\" size=\"4\">! </font></font></font>\n</p>\n","400","1","noimage.jpg","10","");
